.rule_6_10_5_9_ensure_rest_connection_limit_is_set

Reference: tion-statement/connection-limit-edit-system-services-rest.html
rest-api-configuring.html

Remediation: To enable a REST API Connection Limit, enter the following command at the [edit system
services rest] hierarchy:



[edit system services rest]
user@host# set control connection-limit <limit>
Where <limit> is the desired Connection Limit.

.